# memory/.gitignore
# CONSTITUTION §8: All live memory files are gitignored.
# Only *.example files and this .gitignore are committed to version control.
# Never commit personal data, wellbeing logs, or session-specific notes.

# Block all Markdown files in this directory and subdirectories
*.md

# Allow example files (these are committed as templates)
!*.md.example
!**/*.md.example

# Block episodic session files
episodic/*.md
!episodic/*.md.example

# Block semantic memory live files
semantic/*.md
!semantic/*.md.example

# Allow README if present
!README.md
